OL,6,FI'm back at BBC Broadcasting House
OL,7,Fafter the threats against me escalated
OL,8,Fand I stepped away from my job
OL,9,Fpresenting BBC Persian TV's main news
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,FOn 11 January, a colleague at BBC
OL,13,FPersian tells us about a voice message
OL,14,Ffrom a dual national who appears to be
OL,15,Fsentenced to death. The man says he was
OL,16,Ftortured and drugged to confess to
OL,17,Fbeing a British spy.
OL,19,F"A dual national?" I say, looking up
OL,20,Ffrom my laptop. "What is his other
OL,21,Fnationality?"
